metadata.name: Sanitized
metadata.description:
Ah, so you - or someone connected to you - doesn't want you to remember...

Come, sit.

Put on these glasses - they'll animate the room slightly, while playing what should sound like a soft and pleasant white noise.  Really.  Pay these no heed.  Your task is to take one of the picture frames, here, and focus on the images that appear.

Your first session will end when you're no longer able to see anything in the frame - it will simply appear blank.  It shouldn't take more than a few hours.

I'm here to monitor your vitals and keep you safe.  

Restraints shouldn't be necessary.

Let's begin...
